            🛡️ Trusted
          </span>
          <span style="background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.2); border: 1px solid var(--solar-orange); color: var(--solar-orange); padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 15px; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px;">
            ⭐ 5-Star Rated
          </span>
          <span style="background: rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.2); border: 1px solid var(--plasma-cyan); color: var(--plasma-cyan); padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 15px; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px;">
            🏆 Local Experts
